item.g:title: Cream Yellow Net Embroidered Party and Festival Saree
item.g:description: Cream Yellow embroidered party saree intricate with zari thread, keri work, floral work, leaf work and patch patti border. Saree comes with an unstitch blouse piece which can be customised as per your requirement. Customisation includes changing front neck style, back neck style, increasing/reducing the length of sleeves. Accessories which is shown in the image is only for shooting purpose. There might be some color variation. Time to deliver: 15 days. Fall and edging is done to all sarees and it's free of cost.
